videoDetails.Title: BONKING Tanks with HUGE High Explosives  M109 Paladin in War Thunder
videoDetails.Description:
If you're looking to get some GE or a Premium, please use a creators link to support then and get a free decal.  Here's mine:  https://store.gaijin.net/catalog.php?category=WarThunder&partner=Oddbawz&partner_val=2bpa5qx4

Sometimes you just have to HE a fella.  The M109 in War Thunder is the go to SPAG when it comes to deleting anything that is unfortunate enough to drive out in front of you.  With a 155mm cannon and a huge HE shell with 61mm of penetration, this guy can pretty much do it all!

Oh, and if you want to have some real fun... load up a proximity fuse round and swat the enemy from the sky or when they're behind cover!  EXTREMELY fun and very effective.  Maybe... too effective! :)
